paragraphs.title: 3년간 최고가 최저가 저장 table : -Max, -Min, MaxMin
paragraphs.text:
sqlc.sql("""select codeNum,
                max(price) as MAX,
                min(price) as MIN 
            from selectClosingPrice 
            group by codeNum""").toDF().registerTempTable("selectClosingPriceMM")

sqlc.sql("""select o.codeNum,mm.MAX,o.strDate
            from selectClosingPrice o,selectClosingPriceMM mm
            where mm.codeNum = o.codeNum
                AND mm.MAX = o.price""").toDF().registerTempTable("selectClosingPriceMax")
sqlc.sql("""select o.codeNum,mm.MIN,o.strDate
            from selectClosingPrice o,selectClosingPriceMM mm
            where mm.codeNum=o.codeNum 
                AND mm.MIN=o.price""").toDF().registerTempTable("selectClosingPriceMin")
                
sqlc.sql("""select max.codeNum,format_number(max.MAX,0) as MAX,max.strDate as maxDATE,format_number(min.MIN,0) as MIN,min.strDate as minDATE
from selectClosingPriceMax max, selectClosingPriceMin min
where max.codeNum = min.codeNum""").toDF().registerTempTable("selectClosingPriceMaxMintest")
